latestPosts.caption:
The Big Reveal 💕👇🏻

Here’s to ticking off dreams from my wishlist! I’ve always manifested of being on a Billboard and like they say, dreams do come true but life is not so easy for everyone. It was not for me, I had challenges my way.

Everyone has their own struggles, I’ve had my own and I still do. My only source of work/connection was Instagram.. which was suspended in May 2023, I had lost it, i was shattered and left with no hope of my future. My account was suspended for no valid reason (possibly someone got it done intentionally) So, I came back with a New Account and started posting but I had internally given up because it was hard to build everything again! My Mom didn’t let me, she’s been my constant support since the very beginning.

God had my back and Fast Forward to June, I was shooting for a renowned diamond brand for a Billboard! 🥹❤️

I truly believe in NOT GIVING UP, TRYING & BELIEVING. Because one day, it will all make sense ✨🥰
